---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-gray-800 text-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold text-center mb-6">The Ultimate Guide to Taper Fade Haircuts</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-center text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Master the art of the taper fade: From classic styles to modern variations, maintenance tips, and professional insights.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <article class="prose lg:prose-xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-12">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599351431202-1e0f0137899a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
          alt="Taper Fade Haircut"
          class="w-full h-[500px] object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl mb-8"
        />
        
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-12">
          <p class="text-lg text-blue-900">
            The taper fade has revolutionized modern men's hairstyling, combining traditional barbering techniques with contemporary aesthetics. This comprehensive guide will walk you through everything you need to know about this versatile haircut.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Understanding Taper Fades</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">A taper fade is characterized by the gradual transition of hair length, typically starting longer at the top and progressively getting shorter down the sides and back. Unlike regular haircuts, a taper fade requires precise technique and attention to detail to achieve the seamless gradient effect that makes it so appealing.</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 my-12">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Characteristics</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Gradual length transition</li>
              <li>Customizable fade points</li>
              <li>Clean, defined lines</li>
              <li>Versatile styling options</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Benefits</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Professional appearance</li>
              <li>Suits most face shapes</li>
              <li>Easy to maintain</li>
              <li>Adaptable to various styles</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="my-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Types of Taper Fades</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1593702295094-aea22597af65?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Low Taper Fade"
              class="w-full h-80 object-cover"
            />
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4"><a href="https://taperfade.style/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800">Low Taper Fade</a></h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">The low taper fade begins just above the ears, creating a subtle and sophisticated look. This conservative variation is perfect for professional environments while maintaining a modern edge.</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Perfect For:</h4>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
                  <li>Professional settings</li>
                  <li>Conservative environments</li>
                  <li>Easy maintenance</li>
                  <li>Natural growth patterns</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605497788044-5a32c7078486?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Mid Taper Fade"
              class="w-full h-80 object-cover"
            />
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Mid Taper Fade</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Starting at temple level, the mid taper fade offers the perfect balance between subtle and dramatic. This versatile style provides enough contrast to make a statement while remaining professionally acceptable.</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Style Variations:</h4>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
                  <li>Textured top with clean fade</li>
                  <li>Slicked back with fade</li>
                  <li>Pompadour combination</li>
                  <li>Messy top contrast</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1567894340315-735d7c361db0?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" 
              alt="Skin Taper Fade"
              class="w-full h-80 object-cover"
            />
            <div class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Skin Taper Fade</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">The skin taper fade, or bald fade, creates maximum contrast by fading down to the skin. This bold style requires more frequent maintenance but delivers a striking, clean look.</p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Maintenance Tips:</h4>
                <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2">
                  <li>Weekly touch-ups recommended</li>
                  <li>Regular scalp care essential</li>
                  <li>Sun protection necessary</li>
                  <li>Professional maintenance required</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="my-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Professional Styling Guide</h2>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Essential Products</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold">Premium Pomade:</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">For hold and shine</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold">Sea Salt Spray:</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">For natural texture</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold">Matte Clay:</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">For textured finish</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="text-green-500">✓</span>
                <div>
                  <span class="font-semibold">Finishing Spray:</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">For all-day hold</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Styling Steps</h3>
            <ol class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="bg-gray-900 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">1</span>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Start with clean, towel-dried hair</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="bg-gray-900 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">2</span>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Apply styling product evenly</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="bg-gray-900 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">3</span>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Style top section as desired</p>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <span class="bg-gray-900 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">4</span>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Clean up fade lines with a comb</p>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="my-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Maintenance & Care</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-100 to-gray-50 p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Regular Maintenance</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-blue-500">•</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Schedule trims every 2-3 weeks</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-blue-500">•</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Use quality hair products</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-blue-500">•</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Maintain clean hairlines</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-blue-500">•</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Protect from sun damage</p>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Common Mistakes</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-red-500">×</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Skipping regular maintenance</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-red-500">×</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Using wrong products</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-red-500">×</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">DIY fade maintenance</p>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                  <span class="text-red-500">×</span>
                  <p class="text-gray-700">Neglecting scalp care</p>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="my-16">
        <div class="bg-gray-900 text-white p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Pro Tips for Long-Lasting Results</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
              <p>Communicate clearly with your barber about your desired fade height and style</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
              <p>Take photos of your fade when fresh to show your barber for consistency</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
              <p>Invest in quality hair care products specific to your hair type</p>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="text-yellow-400">★</span>
              <p>Consider your lifestyle and maintenance commitment when choosing fade style</p>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: none;
  }
  
  .prose img {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .prose h2 {
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  
  .prose ul, .prose ol {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>